{"tid":349620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求急救]冷氣機向室內漏水","createTime":"2017-08-06T15:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T02:13:01.000Z","uid":75529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06a54c4823905d7716619134eb0b3985169a6d9d","tid":349620,"uid":75529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n今日開冷氣發現滴到自己啲野濕晒<br />\n於是自己研究左陣<br />\n見到機底好多地方都漏水滲水出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好識搞<br />\n所以影底左放上黎請教下應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/230920_3c0b1448fd08e0306586a64b58840b20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F230920_3c0b1448fd08e0306586a64b58840b20.jpg&h=82f1dbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲水由箭咀滲出黎然後直落 btw條m巾係用黎索水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/231119_0283b901d15e2b9e9fe08c528bde0772.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F231119_0283b901d15e2b9e9fe08c528bde0772.jpg&h=a9aef6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry 唔識點focus去後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面個渠位(唔知係咪)啲水好似無郁到 好似係coil啲水都會滴去條渠 正常係去到水？<br />\n<br />\n唔開冷氣真係訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無ching教我點搞"},{"pid":"9598f919c82738ee3ea26992791ac4a597bdb7d6","tid":349620,"uid":14004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"搵嘢墊起佢 傾斜部機向出面排水"},{"pid":"8eda90294525c3b1be318af37baacd5b7c112b55","tid":349620,"uid":117751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:07:28.000Z","msg":"有冇多d info"},{"pid":"1627421616f4616d1a12b594311525410b5ccdbe","tid":349620,"uid":46431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"會唔會係條喉或者個兜塞左，d水無地方去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad2e847d510ad51dd87dd43d3a309794d1492f4","tid":349620,"uid":12720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:10:18.000Z","msg":"比d塵塞晒啦<br />\n一係揾人洗機<br />\n一係換啦 生晒秀"},{"pid":"ae40df9382432ecccd6ffc39c2fa7c6abffcaa6d","tid":349620,"uid":73569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵嘢墊起佢 傾斜部機向出面排水</blockquote><br />\n 咁咪 滴出街<br />\n<br />\n佢搵人清下個去水位仲好啦<br />\n我估係 個度塞左姐<br />\n<br />\n清完再墊高返小小部冷氣"},{"pid":"e75bb98b6aa07fef53d0c9ac56643a2aea824879","tid":349620,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比d塵塞晒啦<br />\n一係揾人洗機<br />\n一係換啦 生晒秀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1667d4e1281185c1982254df80a3ce747bf74d90","tid":349620,"uid":123985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T00:42:06.000Z","msg":"條喉俾塵塞左，一係搵師父洗，一係自己洗，youtube有片教人點清，但好麻煩"},{"pid":"9197c0547e2b8d3d6b4eda812440dabd8ccd1360","tid":349620,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T01:00:45.000Z","msg":"唔好自己搞啦 幾百蚊搵人洗好過 但你個部舊到咁通常都會建議你裝過部"},{"pid":"21ae72bcd79330255f70ad6d324da18363fdbdbc","tid":349620,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s